The,Heap,Analytics,API,provides,developers,a,way,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Heap,Analytics,with,other,applications,The,server,side,API,allows,you,to,send,data,from,your,backend,into,Heap,Some,example,API,methods,include,returning,data,managing,account,information,and,running,data,reports,Heap,Analytics,is,a,service,that,automatically,gathers,information,on,users,and,user,behavior,on,websites,Heap,Analytics,collects,user,data,and,user,behavior,data,such,as,page,views,click,throughs,and,form,submissions